OL,3,C'Indefensible abuse' of rivers
OL,4,Ccriticised by Archbishop of Wales
OL,6,FFor the past six years, she has been
OL,7,Fgathering data on water quality across
OL,8,FWales, and teaching others to do the
OL,9,Fsame.
OL,11,FDescribing the current state of our
OL,12,Fwaterways, Angela dubbed it
OL,13,F"diabolical".
OL,15,FShe said: "We are on the verge of
OL,16,Fecological collapse, our rivers are
OL,17,Fused as open sewers...it is not good
OL,18,Fenough."
