OL,6,FShe welcomed the Church of Wales'
OL,7,Fintervention, saying: "It's absolutely
OL,8,Fmarvellous that the Archbishop has
OL,9,Fcome on board and is supporting what
OL,10,Fwe are all saying because this is
OL,11,Fmother nature and we need that power
OL,12,Fin voices."
